	<div id="kmd" class="modal hide fade" data-backdrop="static" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="kmd_label" aria-hidden="true">
	  <div class="modal-header">
	    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-hidden="true">×</button>
	    <h3 id="kmd_label">WHAT IS KEPLER'S MOVEMENTDASH?</h3>
	  </div>
	  <div class="modal-body">
	    <p>KMD is a movement game that allows students to develop intuition about astronomical concepts like gravity, rotation, orbit, and eccentricity in real-time. After logging in, students are taken to their individualized dashboard. Within their dashboard, they can see the concepts/levels that they have tackled and click to replay or concur the next ones. </p>

		<p>Each level exposes the students to one or two new concepts in astronomy. Once the students finish a level they are given an explanation of how their movement matched the phenomena illustrated.</p>
